      "timestamp": "09:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "对啊，他在上面讲了半小时大局观，PPT 翻得跟走马灯似的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "09:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "结果唯一落到我头上的实句就是这八个字",
