      "timestamp": "09:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "回样品前面坐着呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "09:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "手里捏着那本破实验记录本，我刚才盯着那页面看了半天，笔尖都快把纸戳穿了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "09:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "上面就写了一行字：今天被骂是因为我存在",
