      "role": "User",
      "content": "瓶子越洗越多，洗瓶机一直站在角落当摆件",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "这就叫沟通链路被政治参数切断",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "信号从学生那一层发上去，被亲情滤波器全部截断",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "也就是相关性为零呗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "我这边喊破喉咙，那边连个波形都没有",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "不用算，直接当噪声处理",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "任何从你们嘴里发出的“设备异常”都被映射到“人力可以解决”的那一列",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "你说我要是写匿名信举报这事，会发生什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "最理想的情况是那台洗瓶机终于修好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "最现实的情况是所有人开始猜那封信是谁写的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "然后日常工作里被各种小事卡脖子",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "对，所以你现在不是在纠结设备，而是在评估社交风险",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "而且这种亲戚结构不是一台机子的事",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "涉及采购、报销、考核，一条线绑得死死的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "这就是那种局部自洽、整体崩坏的系统",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "每个人在自己的岗位上都能给出一个看似合理的解释，拼在一起就是灾难",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "你骂得这么顺，是不是你那边也有类似的亲友团？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "程度不一样，但逻辑类似",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "某些核心岗位被一小撮人垄断，外人只能排队等情绪好的一天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "那你会怎么做，如果在我这个位置？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "如果是我，就会先悄悄统计一段时间里因为洗瓶机坏掉浪费的工时",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "再算一次“人力成本”，拿着那个数字在合适的场合扔出去",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "你这是想用他们喜欢的那套语言打脸",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "既然那边只认数字，那就用数字说话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "只不过这事得选时机，说早了会被当成找茬，说晚了你已经累到不想管",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "这标题听着像能发 Nature 的社会学子刊：“洗瓶机瘫痪对课题组产出的影响分析”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "标题可以更刻薄一点",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "不过内容要严谨",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "你可以把那当成一次实验，只不过因变量是人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "人当因变量这件事，本身就挺讽刺",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "科研圈一向如此，只是没人乐意承认",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "15:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "洗完一下午瓶子，现在在休息室吃晚饭",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "桌上是一碗挂逼面",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "汤里浮着几片菜叶那种？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "对，标准配置",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "两片青菜、一点点肉末、一堆面条，再撒一点看不见的味精",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "你这碗的价格是多少？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "校内价，一顿不到十块",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "今天要省着点，毕竟那瓶洗液刚从账上咬走一大块",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "我这边正拧开一罐 Dr. Pepper",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "顺便看一眼刚刚刷到的工资水平调查，心情非常复杂",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "你那一罐糖水钱，够我给这碗面加个顶配浇头了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "不止",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "加蛋加肠再加一包榨菜都够",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "消费体系的汇率真是迷惑",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "但你那罐饮料至少没有跑出鬼峰",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "错，它里面含糖量那叫一个惊人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "血糖曲线足够画一篇论文",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "那你喝的时候会预感以后体检报告上的指标往哪飙？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "会，不过现在更在意的是今天拆板子消耗掉的脑细胞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "喝一点垃圾饮料算补偿",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "你这叫用廉价快乐对冲高价痛苦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "那你那碗面呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "是在为洗液付出的代价做仪式感告别？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "绑定？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "我现在看这碗面都是色谱图",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "青菜是杂质峰，肉末是主峰——虽然面积小得可怜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "经费表上写的每一条数字都在提醒你",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "实验不是在空气里跑的，是在一堆账目之间挪动",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "这也算是另一种“贫穷约束下的最优解”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "只不过解出来的不是理论最优，而是生存最优",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "你刚是不是差点说出那个禁止词？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:10",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "闭嘴，我已经在脑内把那两个字吞回去了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:10",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "行",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:10",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "那我继续端着这碗面假装自己是在做“饮食变量控制实验”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "结果变量是你熬夜耐力",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "还有明天能不能撑到洗液送到",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "17:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "刚看甲在朋友圈发岁月静好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "我就忍不住给他科普了那个老鼠乌托邦实验",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "他现在一脸“这跟现实有啥关系”的表情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "就是那种给老鼠提供无限资源，最后全部变成躺尸的故事？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "对，Calhoun 那套经典实验",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "甲觉得人类不可能那样退化，因为人有道德和目标",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "听着就很理想主义",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "实验室这边物资根本不算富足，照样一堆人躺在系统里当装饰",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "对，我正想说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "那组实验只能说明资源过剩的一种极端情况",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "现实里还有另一种极端：资源贼紧张，但制度设计得像给猪打工",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "你指的是那位去夏威夷的大爷？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "没错",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "他所在的环境资源一点也不少，预算、设备、假期都相当充足",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "最后形成的行为模式是：事情能拖就拖，出问题就自动回复",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "而像我这种",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "资源紧张、时间紧张、胃也紧张",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "只能在一堆约束之下打补丁",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "这就是反向老鼠实验",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "资源紧张到一定程度，群体会退化成只会内斗和造假的状态",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "你这句一针见血",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "最近组内开会，讨论最多的是谁的任务拖慢了，而不是怎么补齐缺口",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "因为直接指出制度问题等于往上拱火",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "content": "大家更偏向横向找替罪羊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "timestamp": "19:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "那你在给甲讲老鼠实验的时候，有没有顺手把你那台板子的事拿出来骂？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
